1
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:44,430
Tie him up tight.

2
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,000
Stop looking. Hurry up.

3
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:28,870
Go get Bai.

4
00:01:31,350 --> 00:01:32,190
Quick.

5
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:06,870
Rest in peace.

6
00:02:11,060 --> 00:02:14,940
=The Hidden Truth=

7
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:17,580
=Episode 8=

8
00:02:40,590 --> 00:02:41,430
Come here.

9
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,310
Listen.

10
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:47,240
Go out the back, now.

11
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,000
Find a crowded place.

12
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:50,800
Let them see you.

13
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,470
The more people, the better. Got it?

14
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:53,310
I'm not leaving.

15
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,190
You have to.

16
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,300
Go. Now.

17
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:56,150
I'm not going.

18
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:57,560
I said I'm not going.

19
00:02:57,970 --> 00:03:00,130
I'm back because I knew
Zhang Ming would be trouble.

20
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:02,000
If he manages to get away,

21
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,000
we're done.

22
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,910
We? What do you mean we're done?

23
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:07,150
Wang Yimo, listen to me.

24
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:08,590
Everything that happened,

25
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,470
I did it all by myself.

26
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,680
It has nothing to do with you.

27
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,520
Got it?

28
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:17,310
Even if something happens to you?

29
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:20,520
Even if I'm left an orphan?

30
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,520
Dad.

31
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,800
Stop carrying everything

32
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,240
by yourself.

33
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:26,840
I can help.

34
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:29,910
Help how?

35
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,280
In my own way.

36
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,080
Dad, tell me the truth.

37
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,030
How much

38
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,360
does Zhang Ming know?

39
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,750
How involved is he?

40
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:43,910
Don't worry about it.

41
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:46,800
He lost control today,

42
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:48,330
was it because of those casino guys

43
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:49,870
who came by earlier?

44
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,870
What happened between you?

45
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:52,710
Stop asking!

46
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,120
Wang Yimo,

47
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,960
I don't want you dragged into this.

48
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,280
The moment you're in trouble,

49
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,560
I was already in it.

50
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,920
Dad,

51
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:09,000
let me help you fix this.

52
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,750
If you won't tell me,

53
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,390
I'll figure it out myself.

54
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:23,910
Wake up.

55
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,760
Ali.

56
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,430
I've done so much for you.

57
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:40,040
I've worked here for years.

58
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,750
You can't do this to me.

59
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,400
Is that so?

60
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,270
Did you consider that

61
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:47,000
when you were stabbing us in the back?

62
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,520
Ming,

63
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:51,310
my dad's treated you well.

64
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,240
Why did you go behind our back

65
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,070
and work with the casino people?

66
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,950
They came to me.

67
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,360
I was forced.

68
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:01,560
If I'd known it'd end like this,

69
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,600
I never would've let him go back then.

70
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:08,800
What are you talking about?

71
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,200
Dad.

72
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,630
What's he talking about?

73
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,720
What did you do?

74
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,190
What did you do?

75
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,840
What's that sound?

76
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:08,630
I steered clear of his head

77
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,800
and kept the dirt thin

78
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:15,000
I thought

79
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,270
let fate decide.

80
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,920
Didn't think he'd actually survive.

81
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:36,680
Zhang Ming.

82
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,840
This whole mess

83
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,750
is because of him.

84
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,830
It's because of me.

85
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:47,000
I followed everything you said.

86
00:06:47,630 --> 00:06:50,120
I just wanted money to save my mom.

87
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:55,240
Murder's too big a crime, Ali.

88
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,950
I didn't dare.

89
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,390
My mom only has me.

90
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,750
If something happens to me,

91
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,800
she's dead for sure.

92
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,310
Murder?

93
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,680
Dad, did you kill someone?

94
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,040
Whom?

95
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,320
Ali…

96
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:20,270
Ali…

97
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,750
Please let me go, Ali.

98
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,750
Ali, I'll do whatever you say.

99
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:24,590
Ali.

100
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,750
Whatever you say.

101
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:27,190
I'll do whatever you tell me to.

102
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:28,040
Please, let me go.

103
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:29,000
I'm begging you, Ali.

104
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:32,480
Dad, we can't let him go.

105
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,270
He knows too much.

106
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,830
Wang Yimo.

107
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:38,240
I did so much for you.

108
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:39,680
You came back

109
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,600
two months early behind his back.

110
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:44,040
You had me hunt dog thieves,

111
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,830
turned the whole city upside down.

112
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:50,240
The Huacai case and the dog thefts

113
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,800
- are unclear.
- Shut up!

114
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:53,560
Now the cops are on me.

115
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,190
You don't help me

116
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:56,720
and dump me when I'm done.

117
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,870
That's cold, Wang Yimo.

118
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,880
See you.

119
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:09,590
Ming,

120
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,160
I know you're under pressure

121
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,160
because of your mom.

122
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,040
If you're in trouble,

123
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,120
talk to my dad anytime.

124
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,800
You've worked here for years.

125
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,750
If we can help, we will.

126
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,750
But you can't steal from the restaurant.

127
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,520
Mr. Zhang.

128
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,400
Dr. Wang.

129
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,040
Here's your mother's treatment bill

130
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,880
for this month.

131
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,500
(Total amount)

132
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,360
Thank you, Dr. Wang.

133
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,150
- No problem.
- Thank you.

134
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,720
I won't tell my dad.

135
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,320
But Ming,

136
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,110
I helped you.

137
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,790
Now you have to help me.

138
00:08:44,090 --> 00:08:44,950
Okay.

139
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,670
My dad doesn't know I'm back yet.

140
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,960
I need you to do a few things for me.

141
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,390
You can't tell anyone.

142
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:51,320
Especially my dad.

143
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,150
If you help me,

144
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,340
I won't say a word

145
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,870
about the accounts.

146
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,630
And I won't interfere with you again.

147
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:01,390
Okay.

148
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,440
Ali,

149
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,350
do you think

150
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:10,080
your daughter doesn't know

151
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,720
what you've arranged for her?

152
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:14,000
She knows everything.

153
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:16,750
Dad.

154
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,200
I'm worried about you.

155
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,200
We agreed

156
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:22,240
you'd sell it and move to Xinjing

157
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,510
to be with me.

158
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:26,030
But then you backed out

159
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,510
and made excuses.

160
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:28,690
You kept me from coming back.

161
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,840
I have to know what happened.

162
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:37,630
I've been used by both of you.

163
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,000
I got nothing.

164
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:43,480
Only blame piled on me.

165
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,750
What you said today,

166
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,390
who else have you told?

167
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,960
Ali,

168
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,000
no one.

169
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:06,440
I never meant to hurt anyone.

170
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:09,670
I've worked for you all these years.

171
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:11,440
Please let me go.

172
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:12,600
Ali.

173
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:13,840
Dad, don't let him go.

174
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,360
Let me go, Ali.

175
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,790
Ali, please. Ali.

176
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,270
Ali... Ali.

177
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:21,670
Help me, Ali.

178
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:24,360
Ali, please have mercy.

179
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:26,030
Please, let me go.

180
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:27,320
Please...

181
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,320
It'll be over soon.

182
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:30,360
Ali.

183
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:31,630
Go in peace.

184
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:17,270
You sure you want to keep him?

185
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,080
We'll talk at home.

186
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:32,540
(Welcome to Hongyun Restaurant)

187
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:45,420
(Ali)

188
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:54,060
(Li Tong)

189
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:56,940
(Li Tong)

190
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,030
To the old house.

191
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,550
The subscriber you dialed
can not be connected.

192
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:19,750
(Ali)
Please leave a message after the tone.

193
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:20,800
Recording done.

194
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,320
Ali?

195
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:46,120
Are you home?

196
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:53,990
Ali?

197
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,840
Dad.

198
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,480
The person Zhang Ming mentioned

199
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:14,910
was Bai, right?

200
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,630
You tried to kill him back then?

201
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,550
Too bad he's still alive.

202
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:28,510
That's why you won't leave.

203
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,670
That's why

204
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:32,110
you won't let me come back.

205
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,440
Dad,

206
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,910
I know everything you did

207
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:40,030
was to protect me.

208
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,240
Especially now, with Bai.

209
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,670
He's been using me to threaten you.

210
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:47,960
But Bai is never satisfied.

211
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:49,270
Every time you give in,

212
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:50,550
he just pushes further.

213
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,560
Dad.

214
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:56,150
I'm not a helpless little girl anymore.

215
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:59,030
I can protect you in my way.

216
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:02,030
So you came back without telling me.

217
00:14:07,350 --> 00:14:08,730
Don't think I don't know anything.

218
00:14:10,870 --> 00:14:12,150
If I hadn't protected you,

219
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:15,080
you'd have been in trouble already.

220
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:16,790
You knew I came back?

221
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:23,390
I know

222
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,200
you wanted to help me.

223
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:27,550
But back then,

224
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,550
I thought

225
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:32,320
I had things under control.

226
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,750
I believed if Bai was dealt with fast,

227
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,670
none of this would've happened.

228
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:41,750
I know you.

229
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,360
Even if I'd asked,

230
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,720
you wouldn't have told me, right?

231
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,750
I found out you met Bai

232
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:50,630
and tracked his movements

233
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:53,480
between the casino and the shelter.

234
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:55,270
I used Zhang Ming,

235
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,960
the dog thieves,

236
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,360
and everyone

237
00:14:58,670 --> 00:15:00,030
just to shift the police's focus

238
00:15:00,030 --> 00:15:01,150
onto Bai.

239
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,870
Only if he was caught would you be safe.

240
00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:17,150
I won't be safe.

241
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:20,600
There's more than just Bai.

242
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:23,440
But you're different.

243
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,240
You're my daughter.

244
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:26,840
You're my everything.

245
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,150
You have to be okay.

246
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,440
But Dad,

247
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:33,240
if anything happens to you,

248
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,440
what do I do?

249
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:38,960
I don't want anything else.

250
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:41,550
I just want a warm home.

251
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,440
You gave me a home.

252
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,150
I can't lose you.

253
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,910
You still have a future.

254
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,360
Stop trying to talk me out of it.

255
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:01,200
I'm already in this.

256
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:06,910
Right now, the priority

257
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:08,840
is fixing what's in front of us.

258
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:12,270
Li Xu answers to Bai too.

259
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:14,440
What exactly is between you?

260
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:23,000
I've already

261
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,840
figured out a solution.

262
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,150
Stay out of it.

263
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,320
This ends here.

264
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:32,960
Dad.

265
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:38,630
From now on,

266
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:40,920
leave it to me.

267
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:51,080
There's a dermatologist
at Third City Hospital.

268
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,910
Great with scar removal.

269
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,440
If you want,

270
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:57,710
I'll go with you.

271
00:16:58,220 --> 00:16:59,070
Give it a try.

272
00:16:59,080 --> 00:16:59,920
It really works.

273
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,680
Yimo,

274
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:04,510
thank you.

275
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:06,110
Trust me.

276
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,830
No matter what happens,

277
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,310
I'll take good care of you both.

278
00:17:16,580 --> 00:17:18,500
(Zhang Ming)

279
00:17:25,350 --> 00:17:26,790
A friend needs me.

280
00:17:26,790 --> 00:17:27,680
I forgot.

281
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,200
I need to go now.

282
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:30,430
That urgent?

283
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:31,360
Yeah.

284
00:17:31,390 --> 00:17:32,400
Ms. Tong, take your time.

285
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,240
I'm heading out.

286
00:17:34,030 --> 00:17:34,870
Be careful.

287
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:56,740
(Debt; Incoming Call)

288
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:06,100
(Debt; Incoming Call)

289
00:18:08,550 --> 00:18:09,390
Hello?

290
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,920
Has the neighbor come back yet?

291
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:13,130
No.

292
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:14,000
I just checked.

293
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,590
They're not answering either.

294
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:19,240
Find out where they went

295
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,750
and what they did.

296
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,310
If they come back,

297
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:24,920
call me immediately.

298
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:45,910
Drink.

299
00:18:47,670 --> 00:18:48,590
I really can't anymore.

300
00:19:05,110 --> 00:19:05,960
Hello, sir.

301
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:12,550
Why aren't you singing?

302
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:17,480
What do you like?

303
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,400
I'll pick one for you.

304
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,150
Relax.

305
00:19:37,830 --> 00:19:38,960
We've met before.

306
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:42,400
I know your line of work.

307
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:44,000
Usually it's

308
00:19:45,240 --> 00:19:46,200
a sick mom,

309
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,160
a gambling dad.

310
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,310
But somehow,

311
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:52,830
you're different.

312
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,750
You look like someone

313
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:02,590
who ran away from the mountains

314
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:06,350
with an abusive husband back home.

315
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:12,310
I don't know what you're talking about.

316
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:22,270
The scars on you

317
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,110
don't lie.

318
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,480
Do what I say,

319
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:32,760
and money

320
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:34,830
won't be a problem.

321
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,640
What do you want me to do?

322
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:39,550
Be clear.

323
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,560
I don't take

324
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:45,520
dirty money.

325
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:49,870
Simple.

326
00:20:50,110 --> 00:20:51,880
Get close to one person.

327
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:54,110
Become familiar.

328
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,640
Tell me

329
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,920
his movements

330
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:00,350
and daily habits.

331
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:03,110
What's your relationship

332
00:21:04,030 --> 00:21:05,070
with him?

333
00:21:05,830 --> 00:21:06,670
Friends.

334
00:21:08,550 --> 00:21:09,550
Best friends.

335
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:11,480
Sorry.

336
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:13,110
New here?

337
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:15,560
Then let me help you.

338
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:17,840
Thanks.

339
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,310
Why do you think

340
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:21,000
I can do this?

341
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:24,350
Because you look just like

342
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,030
his late wife.

343
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:32,830
This face is what I need.

344
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:39,560
Sir,

345
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,110
find someone else.

346
00:21:46,830 --> 00:21:50,920
Dong'an Village, Baijia Town,
Daxishan Township.

347
00:21:51,110 --> 00:21:52,510
The Sun Family.

348
00:21:55,790 --> 00:21:57,510
You think I'm bluffing?

349
00:21:58,110 --> 00:22:00,000
That old jerk surnamed Sun

350
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:01,920
probably doesn't know

351
00:22:03,030 --> 00:22:04,270
you're working here.

352
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:08,000
I heard

353
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:09,880
he swore

354
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:11,240
if he ever found you,

355
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:13,350
he'd kill you.

356
00:22:14,790 --> 00:22:15,630
So,

357
00:22:16,350 --> 00:22:17,550
you still want to walk away?

358
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:42,680
Why aren't you replying?

359
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,920
Don't forget your task.

360
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:48,440
Any news, text me immediately.

361
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:52,440
Or I'll kill you.

362
00:23:02,790 --> 00:23:05,480
I'm watching you.

363
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,310
Remember to call back.

364
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:43,800
Come in.

365
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:02,030
Mr. Wang, you don't look great.

366
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:03,520
So?

367
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,240
Decided yet?

368
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,030
On what?

369
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:09,680
What else?

370
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,270
How to solve the problem.

371
00:24:11,590 --> 00:24:13,110
You wouldn't ask me here so early

372
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:16,350
just to drink tea, right?

373
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,160
Tea quenches thirst.

374
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:22,640
Not sure

375
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:26,720
if it quenches your thirst.

376
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:31,270
Depends what kind of tea you brought.

377
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:42,720
An apartment in the city.

378
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,000
And...

379
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,140
(Property Ownership Certificate)

380
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,680
Hongyun Restaurant.

381
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:58,030
That's some interesting tea.

382
00:24:58,960 --> 00:25:01,270
I know you're generous, Mr. Wang.

383
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:03,350
But this generous?

384
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:05,350
I'm afraid,

385
00:25:05,420 --> 00:25:06,520
it's not just about settling

386
00:25:06,540 --> 00:25:08,030
the issue between the two of us.

387
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:12,880
Today,

388
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:14,550
the real point of this tea,

389
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:15,920
isn't the deal.

390
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:18,920
It's an opportunity.

391
00:25:24,690 --> 00:25:25,800
What kind of opportunity?

392
00:25:30,030 --> 00:25:30,870
This time,

393
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:33,480
Bai used Zhang Ming to make trouble

394
00:25:34,510 --> 00:25:35,880
to drive a wedge

395
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,920
between us

396
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:39,830
and to keep us under his thumb.

397
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,440
But

398
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:46,680
I've run Hongyun for 15 years.

399
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:49,550
It's more than a place to eat.

400
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,830
It's a business.

401
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:53,750
A cover.

402
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:56,030
An identity.

403
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:59,000
A stepping stone.

404
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:03,590
You two

405
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:04,720
have your goals.

406
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:05,590
That's fine.

407
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:07,030
I have mine too.

408
00:26:07,750 --> 00:26:09,400
Then tell me straight.

409
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:11,020
What do I get

410
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,590
out of this?

411
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:14,680
As long as Bai lives,

412
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:20,160
your resources stay scattered.

413
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:22,200
You'll always answer to him.

414
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:25,240
If he falls,

415
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,070
what you take over

416
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:30,480
isn't just a restaurant.

417
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:33,920
It's the whole board.

418
00:26:37,750 --> 00:26:39,400
So you're not asking me

419
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:43,070
to clear out one man,

420
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:48,200
but to run the entire territory.

421
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:52,550
That's tempting.

422
00:26:53,350 --> 00:26:54,190
But

423
00:26:55,030 --> 00:26:56,160
are you really willing

424
00:26:57,000 --> 00:27:00,000
to hand over everything

425
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:03,000
you built all these years?

426
00:27:03,590 --> 00:27:05,510
I planned to leave with my daughter

427
00:27:05,510 --> 00:27:06,720
to travel the world.

428
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:10,510
This is a good moment.

429
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,030
No wonder.

430
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:19,590
So the offer's on the table.

431
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:21,200
Whether you take it

432
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:24,790
depends on how ambitious you are.

433
00:27:30,110 --> 00:27:30,950
Mr. Wang,

434
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,310
your mouth

435
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,880
is way sharper

436
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,550
than the tea you serve.

437
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:43,400
I'm just stating facts.

438
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,310
You know it too.

439
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:58,760
Deal.

440
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:31,440
These days are your Lantern Festival.

441
00:28:31,810 --> 00:28:33,200
I'll make you something nice to eat.

442
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:35,350
Not really my thing, though.

443
00:28:36,590 --> 00:28:38,510
The company wants to talk to you.

444
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:41,160
Why? About what?

445
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:43,240
The livestream money I got from Li Xu...

446
00:28:43,790 --> 00:28:45,310
I already wired it to the company.

447
00:28:45,750 --> 00:28:47,920
The company's request.

448
00:28:51,590 --> 00:28:54,720
The company's request.

449
00:28:57,920 --> 00:28:58,760
Now?

450
00:28:59,220 --> 00:29:01,780
(Unknown Caller)

451
00:29:36,550 --> 00:29:37,390
Yes.

452
00:29:38,030 --> 00:29:38,870
I can hear you.

453
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:42,160
No problems.

454
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:43,190
It's going smoothly.

455
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,920
I'll get more money.

456
00:29:46,750 --> 00:29:48,350
This is just a small part.

457
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:50,800
Yes.

458
00:29:51,960 --> 00:29:53,000
I have a new target.

459
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:54,840
Don't worry.

460
00:31:00,030 --> 00:31:01,000
Fifteen years

461
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:05,440
can change a person

462
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:07,200
completely.

463
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:12,440
Right?

464
00:31:58,310 --> 00:31:59,150
You're awake.

465
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:01,240
Sleep okay?

466
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,350
When did you get back?

467
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:07,200
You didn't come by these days.

468
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:08,400
I thought...

469
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,550
That I just left.

470
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:12,240
That I dumped you.

471
00:32:12,670 --> 00:32:13,670
Didn't need me anymore.

472
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:15,680
So you could

473
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:17,400
cozy up

474
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:19,270
to Wang Li.

475
00:32:19,590 --> 00:32:20,430
Is that it?

476
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:23,830
I'm your eyes and ears.

477
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:26,480
Taking your money,

478
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:28,550
putting on a show with him.

479
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,070
So you know.

480
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:34,950
Sit.

481
00:32:53,030 --> 00:32:53,870
I thought

482
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:55,830
you forgot who you work for.

483
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,790
Living in the place I rented,

484
00:32:57,880 --> 00:33:00,160
doing the job I set up,

485
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,240
taking my pay,

486
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:03,670
and then

487
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:06,030
turning on me.

488
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:25,590
I told you to keep an eye on them.

489
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,040
Where are they?

490
00:33:30,590 --> 00:33:31,590
They didn't come home.

491
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:33,350
So

492
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,270
you just stopped looking?

493
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:39,110
This place made you soft,

494
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:40,520
huh?

495
00:33:43,510 --> 00:33:44,680
I really don't know.

496
00:33:46,110 --> 00:33:47,680
They're not taking my calls.

497
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,240
Call now.

498
00:34:05,020 --> 00:34:08,380
(Ali; Calling)

499
00:34:17,700 --> 00:34:19,700
(Ali)

500
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:21,480
Hello, Li Tong.

501
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,840
Ali.

502
00:34:28,480 --> 00:34:29,670
Where are you and Yimo?

503
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:31,480
Last night,

504
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,230
I baked bread and brought it over.

505
00:34:34,030 --> 00:34:35,230
You weren't home.

506
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:39,920
Family stuff.

507
00:34:40,550 --> 00:34:41,760
We're at a relative's place.

508
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:43,360
It got late, so we didn't go back.

509
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:45,120
Is it serious?

510
00:34:46,070 --> 00:34:48,280
Can you handle it?

511
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:49,680
Thanks.

512
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:52,280
We've got it. Don't worry.

513
00:34:53,230 --> 00:34:54,590
When will you be back?

514
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:57,110
Bread doesn't

515
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,240
keep long.

516
00:34:59,630 --> 00:35:00,760
Not sure yet.

517
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,070
Keep it for now.

518
00:35:04,030 --> 00:35:04,920
Put it in the fridge.

519
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,920
I'll come get it

520
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:07,760
when we're home.

521
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:09,280
Oh, right.

522
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,320
It's windy at night.

523
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,230
Put on something warm.

524
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:16,090
Okay.

525
00:35:16,110 --> 00:35:16,950
Thanks.

526
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:19,250
See you when you're back.

527
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:22,510
Ms. Tong, don't worry about us.

528
00:35:23,630 --> 00:35:26,150
By the way, the scar cream I gave you...

529
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:27,240
Did you use it?

530
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:29,630
It might irritate at first.

531
00:35:29,630 --> 00:35:30,630
Mild reaction.

532
00:35:31,030 --> 00:35:32,320
Stick with it.

533
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:33,630
It works.

534
00:35:36,220 --> 00:35:37,160
I've started using it.

535
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,160
Don't worry.

536
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:39,510
Good.

537
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:40,800
See you soon.

538
00:35:42,070 --> 00:35:42,910
See you.

539
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:47,840
Seems you two aren't that close.

540
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:49,160
He goes places

541
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:51,590
without telling you.

542
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:53,960
They're both

543
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,510
very cautious.

544
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:58,030
Hard to trust anyone.

545
00:36:00,630 --> 00:36:01,470
I think

546
00:36:02,150 --> 00:36:03,510
they didn't tell me the truth.

547
00:36:04,610 --> 00:36:05,950
They're guarding against me.

548
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:10,470
Dad,

549
00:36:12,360 --> 00:36:13,550
there's something

550
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:15,880
you won't want to hear.

551
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,320
But I have to tell you.

552
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,200
You're going to say

553
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:25,280
she was sent

554
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:28,030
by Bai to watch me.

555
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,840
You knew?

556
00:36:33,230 --> 00:36:34,480
How did you find out?

557
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:38,440
Remember when Li Tong got drunk?

558
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:41,150
Her presence never sat right with me.

559
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:43,190
A random neighbor,

560
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:45,840
suddenly all over you for no reason?

561
00:36:46,230 --> 00:36:47,070
Especially

562
00:36:47,670 --> 00:36:49,480
after you began to spiral.

563
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,630
I suspected plenty of people,

564
00:36:52,550 --> 00:36:53,710
her included.

565
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:03,940
(Wang Li was at the restaurant today.
He stayed home today)

566
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,440
(A business dinner)
But I couldn't figure out

567
00:37:05,440 --> 00:37:06,800
(His daughter's back)
who was behind her

568
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:10,150
until that night at the restaurant,

569
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:13,110
when I saw the guy next to Bai.

570
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,200
But Dad,

571
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:17,110
if you knew all along,

572
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:18,800
why get so close to her?

573
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:26,840
Did you expose yourself?

574
00:37:29,110 --> 00:37:31,000
No. I was careful.

575
00:37:31,840 --> 00:37:32,680
This

576
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:35,360
is your only value.

577
00:37:37,710 --> 00:37:40,510
If you mess this up...

578
00:37:40,670 --> 00:37:42,030
I know the consequences.

579
00:37:43,590 --> 00:37:44,800
What really happened

580
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,590
between you and Wang Li

581
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:51,030
that you hate him this much?

582
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:55,680
Curious, huh?

583
00:38:00,110 --> 00:38:00,950
You're not

584
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:04,320
taking him out, are you?

585
00:38:38,550 --> 00:38:40,000
Let's go back later.

586
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:42,280
Li Tong called already.

587
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:44,510
If we stay away too long,

588
00:38:45,670 --> 00:38:46,960
Bai will get suspicious.

589
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:49,120
Right now,

590
00:38:49,590 --> 00:38:50,670
we need him to think

591
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,150
he still controls us.

592
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:56,240
Okay.

593
00:38:58,110 --> 00:38:58,950
Dad,

594
00:38:59,320 --> 00:39:00,920
you said you had a solution.

595
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,400
What is it?

596
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,880
Didn't we agree already?

597
00:39:07,510 --> 00:39:08,350
From here on,

598
00:39:10,110 --> 00:39:11,030
I'll handle it.

599
00:39:13,630 --> 00:39:14,550
You stay out.

600
00:39:30,070 --> 00:39:31,150
I noticed you

601
00:39:31,710 --> 00:39:34,110
keep bumping into corners.

602
00:39:34,630 --> 00:39:35,800
All bruised up.

603
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:38,000
With these corner guards,

604
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:39,430
you won't

605
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:41,630
get hurt anymore.

606
00:39:45,030 --> 00:39:45,920
Thanks, Ali.

607
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:47,640
No need.

608
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:05,230
If the restaurant were gone,

609
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:06,920
would you be disappointed?

610
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,320
That'd be good.

611
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:11,320
If it's gone,

612
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:13,190
the only thing tying you down is me.

613
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:15,510
We could go anywhere.

614
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:18,000
And you won't keep nagging

615
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,400
how the restaurant needs you.

616
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,510
Once this is over,

617
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:24,840
I'm taking you

618
00:40:25,630 --> 00:40:26,920
to travel the world.

619
00:40:48,640 --> 00:40:54,130
♪Dreams of the past sleep in the chill♪

620
00:40:54,130 --> 00:40:57,580
♪Now I run toward the light♪

621
00:40:59,430 --> 00:41:04,690
♪What does the fire burn,
what does it reveal?♪

622
00:41:05,010 --> 00:41:08,660
♪Is the answer found when the sun rises♪

623
00:41:09,270 --> 00:41:13,560
♪If it's all a lie♪

624
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:18,920
♪Should I tear it open?♪

625
00:41:20,250 --> 00:41:24,970
♪If it's all part of the journey♪

626
00:41:25,650 --> 00:41:30,500
♪Then face the blaze head-on♪

627
00:41:30,890 --> 00:41:35,360
♪Let the sun awaken my heart's crave♪

628
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:41,630
♪Pain reminds me I'm alive♪

629
00:41:41,750 --> 00:41:46,560
♪The world can't take away every clear sky♪

630
00:41:47,210 --> 00:41:52,360
♪The hotter it gets, the fiercer I fight♪

631
00:41:52,670 --> 00:41:57,390
♪Let the sun burn away all I lean upon♪

632
00:41:57,730 --> 00:42:03,390
♪Leave me only what endures♪

633
00:42:03,500 --> 00:42:09,050
♪At the cliff's edge, all fear shatters♪

634
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:16,060
♪With a grounded heart, a soul like fire♪
